{"tid":701714,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"再有內地女子涉高院庭內拍照　疑犯遭保安截停　司法機構報警","createTime":"2018-06-14T10:35:51.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-14T13:27:29.000Z","uid":89595,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"8781a7c375c45574910a42cb42c63707ff6e9dd3","tid":701714,"uid":89595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-14T10:35:51.000Z","msg":"高等法院再發生懷疑有人在庭內拍攝事件。高院11樓27庭今早處理一宗毒品案件時，一名中年女子疑在開庭前，在法庭內舉起手機拍攝。女子離庭時遭保安截停，經查問後，司法機構報警求助。據了解，該女子操普通話，為一名內地人。<br />\n<br />\n據處理案件的辯方大律師指，其暑期學生今早在27庭等候開庭期間，見到一名女子高舉手機拍攝，但不清楚該女子開庭期間有否繼續拍攝，亦不清楚女子拍攝了多少張相片。法官判刑後，女子離開法庭，但被保安截停。女子遭查問後，司法機構決定報警處理。<br />\n<br />\n高院近月發生多宗懷疑有人在庭內拍攝的事件，其中內地女子唐琳玲被裁定刑事藐視法庭罪成，判囚7日。高院各法庭近日在開庭前，均改以廣東話、英語及普通話作廣播，提醒公眾在庭內不得拍攝。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180614/s00001/1528968327417\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180614%2Fs00001%2F1528968327417&d=sX8bL84bYpOGpKt1KXoOY%2F755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=8b00696f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180614%2Fs00001%2F1528968327417&h=15ad91bd\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180614/s00001/1528968327417</a><blockquote><br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180614/s00001/1528\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180614%2Fs00001%2F1528&d=sX8bL84bYpOGpKt1KXoOY%2F755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=09428d0e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180614%2Fs00001%2F1528&h=0e3a0625\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180614/s00001/1528</a></blockquote>"},{"pid":"e3138f67cdf74894cf34ee37d2916117647c4dc2","tid":701714,"uid":89595,"like":0,"dislike"